data.description:
''Exceptional Curb Appeal and Versatile Living Space'' Located in a  super friendly 55 + community
Home offers a Completely remodeled kitchen w/ new cabinets, countertops. . Notably, the professionally enclosed and finished Arizona Room adds substantial living space, and it's worth noting that this room is not included in the official square footage.
Inside, the home boasts an open and airy layout that seamlessly connects the kitchen, dining area, and living room, creating a welcoming atmosphere. You'll find two generously sized bedrooms, and the Arizona Room provides endless possibilities, whether you need a den, extra bedroom, or a hobby/game area. Hurry before this one is gone! Kitchen is also equipped with numerous convenient features, including a handy spice rack in the pantry and natural light from window. Ceiling fans are thoughtfully placed throughout the home for comfort.
Enjoy the preferred North-South exposure, which enhances energy efficiency. In the backyard, a professionally installed slab is ready to support a shade structure, allowing for outdoor relaxation.
Additional amenities include an interior laundry room and a two-car garage.  Community amenities include pools, sports courts, golf, and more. Don't miss out on this opportunity to experience superior retirement living!
